<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>    Torpor:</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->  This incredible 60th level but uncommon regeneration buff cures 1200 HP for 200 mana, in 4 ticks.  While it has various side effects, such as snare, slow, and the target loses <!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><u>50 mana</u><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END-->, it is the best spell to use with rods.  Under the influence of <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>    Torpor</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->, one regenerates 300 HP per tick, enough to eat one charge on a rod.  This spell allows you to attain a state I called <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>    Frenzied Transvergence</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->, where the <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>    Magician</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> burns their mana bar as fast as they can press their spell gems, and never let their buttocks touch the floor.<br>
<br>
For example, in four ticks, a <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>    Magician</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> could produce four rods, eating a charge on each before dropping them, for zero HP cost, and a net mana cost of 4 x (360 - 220) or 480 mana.  This is not counting any other regeneration effects, at least some of which do stack with <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>    Torpor</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->.  With only a little more regeneration and healing, the <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>    Magician</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> becomes a mana machine, and need not only produce rods.<br>
<br>
However, you are unlikely to see <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>    Torpor</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> outside a raid.  <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>    Shaman</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> are in demand by all groups, and are especially beloved by melees for slow.  It also requires being in the same group as the shaman, so on a raid, <!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><u>insist</u><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END--> that you are grouped with the shaman with <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>    Torpor</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->.  It will make rodding so much more efficient, and free up your mana to do other things as well.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> EDIT:</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> Changed <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> &quot;50% mana&quot;</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> to <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> &quot;50 mana.&quot;</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
